#. settings-schema.json->process-name->description
msgid ""
"Name of process or PID to be monitored (by default, the Cinnamon process is "
"used)"
msgstr ""
"Navn på proces eller PID der skal overvåges (som standard bruges Cinnamon-"
"processen)"

#. settings-schema.json->process-name->tooltip
msgid ""
"Set the name of the process or PID you want to monitor here.\n"
"Note that, for the moment, no consideration is given to multiple instances "
"of the same program (undefined behavior).\n"
"Open the system monitor to see all running processes."
msgstr ""
"Angiv her navnet på den proces eller PID, du vil overvåge.\n"
"Bemærk, at der foreløbig ikke tages højde for flere forekomster af det "
"samme program (udefineret adfærd).\n"
"Åbn systemovervågningen for at se alle kørende processer."

